andidates at all levels of government. In 2015, he left NORML to explore other political issue activism including campaign finance reform and tax policy. He returned to NORML as executive director in 2016 and presently continues to serve in that role.<ref name=\"auto\"/>\n\n== References ==\n<ref>{{cite web |url=https://news.vice.com/en_ca/article/9knqgz/it-looks-like-jeff-sessions-is-kicking-off-his-war-on-legal-weed |website=news.vice.com |publisher=[[Vice News]] |title=It looks like Jeff Sessions is kicking off his war on legal weed |access-date=2018-11-02 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181002080701/https://news.vice.com/en_ca/article/9knqgz/it-looks-like-jeff-sessions-is-kicking-off-his-war-on-legal-weed# |archive-date=2018-10-02 |url-status=live }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.businessinsider.in/Canada-just-became-the-second-country-in-the-world-to-legalize-marijuana/articleshow/64669157.cms |website=businessinsider.in |publisher=[[Business Insider India]] |title=Canada just became the second country in the world to legalize marijuana |access-date=2018-11-02 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180917063448/https://www.businessinsider.in/canada-just-became-the-second-country-in-the-world-to-legalize-marijuana/articleshow/64669157.cms# |archive-date=2018-09-17 |url-status=live }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.mynews13.com/fl/orlando/politics/2018/07/27/studying-the-marijuana-effect--new-bill-calls-for-research-where-pot-is-legal |website=mynews13.com |publisher=[[News 13]] |title=Studying the marijuana effect: New bill calls for research where pot is legal |access-date=2018-11-02 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181107214941/http://www.mynews13.com/fl/orlando/politics/2018/07/27/studying-the-marijuana-effect--new-bill-calls-for-research-where-pot-is-legal# |archive-date=2018-11-07 |url-status=live }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.washingtontimes.com/news/2018/apr/11/john-boehner-joins-cannabis-dispensary-board