/player.php?id=84&level=ss21 Republic of Ireland profile] at Soccer Scene\n\n{{Accrington Stanley F.C. squad}}\n\n{{DEFAULTSORT:Conneely, Seamus}}\n[[Category:1988 births]]\n[[Category:Living people]]\n[[Category:Footballers from Lambeth]]\n[[Category:English footballers]]\n[[Category:Republic of Ireland association footballers]]\n[[Category:Republic of Ireland under-21 international footballers]]\n[[Category:Republic of Ireland under-23 international footballers]]\n[[Category:Association football defenders]]\n[[Category:Association football midfielders]]\n[[Category:Mervue United A.F.C. players]]\n[[Category:Galway United F.C. (1937\u20132011) players]]\n[[Category:Sheffield United F.C. players]]\n[[Category:Alfreton Town F.C. players]]\n[[Category:Sligo Rovers F.C. players]]\n[[Category:Accrington Stanley F.C. players]]\n[[Category:League of Ireland players]]\n[[Category:English Football League players]]\n[[Category:National League (English football) players]]\n", "text_old": "{{EngvarB|date=July 2013}}\n{{Use dmy dates|date=July 2013}}\n{{Infobox football biography\n| name              = Seamus Conneely\n| image             =\n| caption           =\n| fullname          = Seamus Joseph Conneely<ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.efl.com/siteassets/image/201920/general-news/efl-squad-numbering-06.09.2019.pdf |title=Notification of shirt numbers: Accrington Stanley |publisher=English Football League |page=1 |accessdate=16 October 2019}}</ref>\n| birth_date        = {{birth date and age|1988|7|9|df=y}}<ref name=Hugman>{{Hugman|26570|accessdate=16 October 2019}}</ref>\n| birth_place       = [[Lambeth]], England<ref name=Hugman/>\n| currentclub       = [[Accrington Stanley F.C.|Accrington Stanley]]\n| clubnumber        = 28\n| height            = {{convert|1.85|m|ftin|0|abbr=on}}\n| position          = [[Midfielder]]<br />\n| youthyears1       = | youthclubs1 = [[Mervue United A.F.C.|Mervue United]]\n| years1 = 2007\u20132011  | clubs1 = [[Galway United F.C.|Galway United